854
01:20:44,838 --> 01:20:48,592
我们去吃饭吧 这些事都丢一边吧
Let's have dinner and put all this mess behind us.

855
01:20:50,010 --> 01:20:53,472
- 9.00, 在Vieux Moulin见,好吗? - 听上去不错
- 9.00, Vieux Moulin. OK? - That sounds great.

856
01:20:54,556 --> 01:20:56,308
我很期待我们的谈话
I miss our conversations.

857
01:20:56,433 --> 01:20:58,769
是Vieux Moulin
Vieux Moulin it is.

858
01:20:59,645 --> 01:21:04,149
好吧,那我叫凤和她姐姐吃饭
All right, then. I'll tell Phuong she can have dinner with her sister.

859
01:21:04,900 --> 01:21:06,777
我叫她吃完饭来见我
I'll get her to meet me here afterwards.

860
01:21:12,908 --> 01:21:16,912
如果你不认识,直接来这儿
Look, if you can't make it, come straight here.

861
01:21:17,997 --> 01:21:19,623
- 我会等你的 - 好的
- I'll wait for you. - All right.

862
01:21:19,790 --> 01:21:22,376
一会见,托马斯
I'll see you soon, Thomas.

863
01:23:08,482 --> 01:23:10,567
走
Walk.

864
01:23:20,619 --> 01:23:23,539
我得跟会说英语的人聊聊
I need to talk to somebody who speaks English.

865
01:23:24,832 --> 01:23:27,751
你知道吗,今晚是我儿子的生日
You see, it's my son's birthday tonight.

866
01:23:35,467 --> 01:23:38,178
我们要问你几个问题
We need to ask you some questions.

867
01:23:38,345 --> 01:23:41,932
我是美国公使馆的 我只是帮人治眼睛的
I'm from the American legation. I just try and help people see.

868
01:23:46,520 --> 01:23:48,063
但问题是...
The thing is, l...

869
01:23:48,230 --> 01:23:51,608
我收到妻子的电报
I got a cable from my wife.

870
01:23:55,029 --> 01:24:00,159
我儿子得了小儿麻痹 他们不知道他挺不挺得过去
My boy has polio. They don't know if he's going to make it.

871
01:24:03,871 --> 01:24:05,664
我不介意他残废
I don't care if he's crippled.

872
01:24:05,831 --> 01:24:08,042
只要他别死
I just don't want him to die.

873
01:24:50,042 --> 01:24:52,544
我很抱歉,我得去透透气
I'm sorry. I've just got to get some air.

874
01:25:39,049 --> 01:25:44,179
至少2000人死亡,还有更多受伤
At least 2,000 people were killed and scores of others injured.

875
01:25:44,305 --> 01:25:46,557
上星期在西贡的爆炸事件中
In the wake of last week's bomb blast in Saigon,

876
01:25:46,974 --> 01:25:49,476
法国官方报道...
French officials report...

877
01:25:57,359 --> 01:25:59,361
很抱歉打扰你,但...
I'm sorry to bother you, but...

878
01:25:59,528 --> 01:26:01,864
你介意和我一起下楼吗?
would you mind to come downstairs with me?

879
01:26:02,906 --> 01:26:06,618
- 你想怎样? - 我要给你看点东西
- What do you want? - I have something to show you.

880
01:26:08,537 --> 01:26:12,708
似乎派尔先生死那晚来见过你
It seems Monsieur Pyle came to see you the night he died.

881
01:26:13,625 --> 01:26:16,170
- 那又怎样? - 你说他没来过
- So what, Vigot? - You said he did not.

882
01:26:19,340 --> 01:26:23,052
还有,我们找到派尔的狗
By the way, we found Pyle's dog.

883
01:26:23,218 --> 01:26:25,512
他们割段了他的喉咙
They cut its throat.

884
01:26:28,807 --> 01:26:30,851
你看到吗?
You see here?

885
01:26:31,018 --> 01:26:34,313
派尔的狗脚趾间有水泥
Pyle's dog had cement between its toes.

886
01:26:34,480 --> 01:26:37,858
这的水泥是他被杀那天下午浇得
This was poured on the afternoon of his murder.

887
01:26:38,025 --> 01:26:40,027
那能说明什么?
So what does that prove?

888
01:26:42,571 --> 01:26:45,658
还有Vieux Moulin 饭店的老板告诉我
And the patron of the Vieux Moulin told me

889
01:26:45,783 --> 01:26:50,329
那晚你只要了一个位子
that night you asked for a table for one.

890
01:26:50,954 --> 01:26:52,414
而不是两个
Not two.

891
01:26:53,791 --> 01:26:56,919
我对于我最初的口供没任何可再说的
I have nothing more to add to my original statement.

892
01:27:00,172 --> 01:27:01,715
没有?
Nothing?

893
01:27:07,012 --> 01:27:09,014
你知道不是我杀他的
You know I didn't kill him, Vigot.

894
01:27:14,687 --> 01:27:17,022
现在是战争年代
There's a war on.

895
01:27:17,147 --> 01:27:19,066
每天都有人死
People are dying every day.

896
01:28:40,814 --> 01:28:43,275
找别的女孩
Ask another girl.

897
01:28:44,610 --> 01:28:46,528
我不想找别的女孩
I don't want another girl.

898
01:29:17,601 --> 01:29:20,896
你能回到我身边吗,凤?
Will you come back now, Phuong?

899
01:29:21,063 --> 01:29:23,732
- 你能回到我身边吗? - 回伦敦?
- Will you come back to me? - To London?

900
01:29:24,942 --> 01:29:27,528
不,不回伦敦
No. Not to London.

901
01:29:29,822 --> 01:29:32,157
那我不会回来的
Then I don't come back.

902
01:29:32,324 --> 01:29:34,785
拜托,我...
Please. I...

903
01:29:36,036 --> 01:29:38,038
我不能带你去伦敦
I can't take you to London.

904
01:29:38,914 --> 01:29:41,333
因为我不去那儿
Because I'm not going.

905
01:29:43,002 --> 01:29:45,004
我不会离开你
I'm not leaving you.

906
01:29:52,094 --> 01:29:53,304
永远不
Never.

907
01:29:56,181 --> 01:29:58,726
你能回来我身边吗?
Will you come back to me?

908
01:30:33,719 --> 01:30:37,056
- 能帮我拆头发吗? - 好的
- Will you take down my hair? - Yes.

909
01:30:56,075 --> 01:30:58,160
你想他吗?
Do you miss him?

910
01:31:05,376 --> 01:31:07,586
是的
Yes.

911
01:31:08,962 --> 01:31:10,589
我很抱歉
I'm sorry.

912
01:31:13,092 --> 01:31:15,594
为什么抱歉?
Why are you sorry?

913
01:31:16,303 --> 01:31:18,347
我不知道
I don't know.

914
01:31:19,473 --> 01:31:21,850
我只是觉得...
I just feel that...

915
01:31:22,017 --> 01:31:25,145
我应该向....谁道歉
I ought to apologise to... someone.

916
01:31:29,191 --> 01:31:31,193
不是我
Not to me.

917
01:31:32,069 --> 01:31:33,696
永远不会是我
Never to me.

918
01:31:42,538 --> 01:31:44,832
人们说你来到越南
They say you come to Vietnam

919
01:31:44,999 --> 01:31:48,711
你会立即明白很多事
and understand a lot in a few minutes.

920
01:31:48,877 --> 01:31:53,340
剩下的得自己去体验
The rest has got to be lived.

921
01:31:53,507 --> 01:31:56,051
他们说不管你寻求什么
They say whatever it was you were looking for

922
01:31:56,885 --> 01:31:58,887
你都能在这如愿以偿
you will find here.

923
01:31:59,888 --> 01:32:03,976
人们说每间房里都有鬼魂
They say there is a ghost in every house.

924
01:32:04,852 --> 01:32:07,354
如果你能和他和平共处
And if you can make peace with him,

925
01:32:07,521 --> 01:32:09,481
他会很安静
he will stay quiet.